{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebuttoncomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of buttons","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"button"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSButton"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ButtonComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"buttons"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Button"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"), borders"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"kind":"symbol","topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:borders:colors:spaces:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider\/borders","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider\/colors","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider\/sizes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider\/ButtonComponentTokens-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/AllButtonComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent06ButtonB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/TokensProvider"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for button component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the button component tokens you want.","","        override var buttonSizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.dimension600 }","","        override var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.borderWidthThicker }","","        override var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.borderRadiusMedium }","","        override var buttonColorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.colorRepositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","","        override var buttonSpacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.spacePaddingInlineSpacious }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider: ButtonComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, you can give this ","type":"text"},{"code":"CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to your own theme implementation:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(button: CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    OrangeTheme(button: CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let buttonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, borders, colors and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let buttonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider","                                                spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.9.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B34ThemeButtonComponentTokensProviderC","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"references":{"doc://OUDS/documentation/OUDS/TokensProvider":{"title":"Tok